headline: A Look At Mosaic (MOS) Valuation As Shares Cool After Recent Pullback
summary: Mosaic (MOS) has drawn investor attention after recent price moves, with the stock closing at US$28.73 as its fertilizer focused business continues to trade around mixed short term and longer term return figures. See our latest analysis for Mosaic. The recent pullback, including a 2.38% 1 day share price return and softer 7 day performance, comes after a stronger 90 day share price return of 18.92% and a 1 year total shareholder return of 16.96%. This suggests that momentum has cooled...

headline: Mosaic: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: On a per-share basis, the Tampa, Florida-based company said it had a loss of $1.64. Earnings, adjusted for non-recurring costs, came to 22 cents per share. The results missed Wall Street expectations.
